		{"id":"df273c3cb96cd9a2","type":"text","text":"💬 **[固定訊息] 確認訂金收款**\n人工更新資料","x":30,"y":336,"width":280,"height":80,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"752d0f184d0a916a","type":"text","text":"**用私人管理帳號拉群組**\n群組名稱=市府訂單ID","x":30,"y":456,"width":280,"height":80,"color":"3"},
